<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <%- include('partials/header1.ejs') %>
    <!-- Add custom CSS for additional styling -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar1.ejs') %>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="jumbotron mt-3">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to GardenGrocer!</h1>
            <p class="lead">At GardenGrocer, we're all about making fresh, affordable food accessible to everyone in Porirua Wellington. Whether you're looking for fruits, veggies, or pantry staples, we've got you covered with top-quality products at great prices.</p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <p>Feel free to browse our extensive product catalog without any login requirements. You'll see real-time stock updates, prices, and current promotions. For an even better shopping experience, log in to unlock personalized discounts!</p>
            <p class="lead">
                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/login" role="button">Login</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="/public/images/home.jpg" alt="Fresh Groceries">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Explore Our Products</h2>
                <p>From farm-fresh produce to everyday household essentials, we have everything you need. Our products come from trusted suppliers and are rigorously checked for quality and freshness.</p>
                <p>Shop with confidence and discover great deals every day at GardenGrocer!</p>
                <a class="btn btn-success" href="/products" role="button">Browse Products</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
    <!-- Add Bootstrap JS (Optional, if needed) -->
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
